Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.cards

Class TargetsFilters

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.model.cards.TargetsFilters
  • public class TargetsFilters
extends java.lang.Object
    This class features a width number of public static methods that filter which Players or Squares can be targeted. Those methods are all called when a weapon or a weapon card is selected.
